                    <p class="text-justify mb-3">By implementing remote monitoring solutions, CCTV businesses can gain real-time insights into the performance of their surveillance systems. These solutions enable continuous monitoring of key parameters such as camera connectivity, video quality, and storage capacity. In the event of any abnormalities, alerts can be generated, notifying technicians of the issue so that they can take immediate action.</p>
